### 2.3 PHCA and BPA: Hierarchical Validation Frameworks

- **Perceptual‑Hierarchical Consistency Analysis (PHCA):** checks whether changes in lower‑level parameters (e.g., attentional stability, nucleotide mismatch rate) hierarchically predict changes in higher‑level outcomes (e.g., system coherence, organismal fitness). It is derived from the Proclean hierarchical constraint algorithm.
